# Reuse Svelte Components

When developing anything, check if there are Svelte components implemented already that can be used instead.

## Guidelines

- Before creating a new component, search `src/lib/components/` for existing ones
- Prefer composing from `ui/` primitives (Button, Field, ButtonGroup, etc.) and shared components
- Only add new components when no suitable existing component exists or can be extended

## Examples

```svelte
<!-- ❌ BAD - new button when Button.svelte exists -->
<button class="px-4 py-2 rounded">Submit</button>

<!-- ✅ GOOD - reuse existing component -->
<Button>Submit</Button>
```
